strong.span:
The Knowledge Bowl team won the regional competition in Thief River Falls on Wednesday, March 11
earning their second consecutive trip to the state competition. The state competition will be held April 2-3. Team members are Ben Brantner, Ainsley Boucher, Emily Gillette, Scott Cordova, and Walker Winjum.

p.span: I wanted to communicate Crookstons preparations to combat the spread of COVID-19 (coronavirus) as this is something that many parents may have questions on. I want to start by assuring you that the district put into place infection prevention procedures once a confirmed cases of coronavirus was reported in MN. The Minnesota Department of Health along with the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention are monitoring and providing guidance to MN Public Schools. We continue to look for guidance and direction on this emerging situation from the MN Department of Health and our local Public Health Department. Continue reading
